(Ford go bike trip dataset analysis)¶

by (Abdalla Omar)¶

This data set includes information about trip data in a bike sharing system covering San Francisco.¶

It contains trip duration, trip start and end times, trip start and end stations, along with user type, gender and their age

We are going to find answers about average trip duration, What are most start stations? Does age affect trip duration? does user type or gender affect both?¶

the structure of your dataset¶

The dataset constructed of 174952 row and 9 column

the main feature(s) of interest in your dataset¶

duration,Start times,end times,gender and user type

features in the dataset do you think will help support your investigation into your feature(s) of interest¶

Duration will help in figuring out the average trip time. Also the most start times. user_type and gender will give me insight about thier effect on the previous statistics
